      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is\u2014it's basically been living in a bubble! I've taken such good care of it, and it still has that brand-new feel inside and out. Not a scratch or a dent to be found, and it drives like an absolute dream. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
