    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2002 BMW M3 (E46) represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Power is derived from the S54 3.2-liter inline-six, featuring a double-VANOS variable valve timing system and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring precise power delivery. The chassis integrity is superlative, with documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension setup that retains its original damping characteristics and bushing compliance. The exterior finish is flawless, showing no signs of oxidation or road rash, while the interior maintains its factory-fresh tactile quality. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
