    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'pre-owned.' This car is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating applied to ensure long-term protection; you won't find a single rock chip or swirl mark on the body. Inside, the cabin remains pristine, still carrying that new-car scent. The premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear on the bolsters, and every electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is flawless. It comes with a complete, documented service history from authorized dealerships, including a recent comprehensive inspection and fluid flush. With exceptionally low mileage and brand-new performance tires, it drives with the precision and smoothness of a brand-new vehicle. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been pampered by a single enthusiast owner. Includes all original manuals, two master keys, and a custom-fit car cover.",
